Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:59.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:06.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:15.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:30.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.23,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.48,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.02,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.07,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:29.74,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失准的时钟 记录着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.62,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}散落满地的记忆之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:37.50,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:42.47,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看 却是那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.76,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.02,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望能与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.10,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.15,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:59.65,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不再失去曾经拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:06.49,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我忘却自己的过去 重新开始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.70,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.79,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:15.21,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿那让你苦不堪言的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.80,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}会迎来完结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.42,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我却要目送你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.84,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.89,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:30.97,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.56,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.73,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.15,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手迈进
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Title——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.90,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,620)\fsp5\c&HFFFFFF&}遥不可及的约{\c&HFFD7AB&}定{\c&HFFFFFF&}之晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs+3\pos(1030,404)\c&HAD6B77&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6}D{\fs-3}mg{\r\c&H000000&\fn方正准圆_GBK\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6}:{\r\c&H000000&}        {\fn方正小标宋_GBK\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6}国\N\N\h\h\h\h\h{\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK}        {\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs-1}组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\pos(1046,275)}动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\pos(1109,300)}漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\fs-1\pos(1129,393)}字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\fs-1\pos(1188,417)}幕
